item.goety.zpiglin_brute_servant_spawn_e: Zombified Piglin Brute Servant Spawn Egg
item.goety.focus.info: When Cast in Wand or Staff:
item.goety.vexing_focus.info: Summons allied Vexes. Cast crouching will kill all the caster's Vexes.
item.goety.biting_focus.info: Summons a row of magic Fangs in front of caster. Cast crouching will summon Fangs around the caster.
item.goety.rotting_focus.info: Summons Zombie Servants. Cast crouching will summon the caster's servants towards them.
item.goety.osseous_focus.info: Summons Skeleton Servants. Cast crouching will summon the caster's servants towards them.
item.goety.spooky_focus.info: Summons Wraith Servants. Cast crouching will summon the caster's servants towards them.
item.goety.vanguard_focus.info: Summons Vanguard Servants. Cast crouching will summon the caster's servants towards them.
item.goety.skull_focus.info: Summons Haunted Skulls. Cast crouching will summon the caster's skulls towards them.
item.goety.wither_skull_focus.info: Shoots a Wither Skull in front of the caster. Cast crouching will shoot a blue skull that's slower but more destructive.
item.goety.ghastly_focus.info: Summons Mini-Ghasts. Cast crouching will dismiss all allied Mini-Ghasts.
item.goety.blazing_focus.info: Summons Blaze Servants. Cast crouching will summon the caster's servants towards them.
item.goety.iceology_focus.info: Summons an Ice Chunk above a location or non-allied target. Ice Chunk will fall after a time stunning and slowing entities below it.
item.goety.frost_nova_focus.info: Summons a non-destructive frost explosion on the caster, or on a target if crouch casting, knocking back and freezing nearby non-allied targets.
item.goety.frostborn_focus.info: Summons an Ice Golem. Cast crouching will summon the caster's servants towards them.
item.goety.barricade_focus.info: Summons Totemic Walls at a location or surrounding a target. Cast crouching will summon Totemic Bombs, that will explode after a time.
item.goety.quaking_focus.info: Sends tremors in front of the caster, damaging and flinging non-allied entities. Cast crouching will summon tremors around the caster.
item.goety.pulverize_focus.info: Transforms certain blocks into another when right-clicked on them, ie. Cobblestone to Gravel.
item.goety.rotation_focus.info: Right-clicking on certain block rotates its orientation or direction.
item.goety.scatter_focus.info: Summons Scatter Mines around the caster, that will let out a non-destructive explosion if a non-allied target enters its area.
item.goety.eruption_focus.info: Summons a small volcano at a location which will shoot several flaming rocks at the sky.
item.goety.illusion_focus.info: Summons Dopplegangers of the caster. Cast crouching will dismiss all allied Dopplegangers.
item.goety.feast_focus.info: Summons a magic Fang on any nearby mob or player that's not the caster.
item.goety.teeth_focus.info: Summons a magic Tooth above a location or non-allied target. After a time, it will fall towards the ground, damaging and flinging targets below.
item.goety.fire_breath_focus.info: Shoots a torrent of soul fire in front of them, burning non-allied and non fire-immune targets.
item.goety.fireball_focus.info: Shoots a small Fireball that damages non fire-immune targets.
item.goety.lavaball_focus.info: Shoots a Lava Bomb. Cast crouching will make the Lava Bomb non-destructive on terrain.
item.goety.magma_bomb_focus.info: Shoots a Magma Bomb, which would explode and spawn several loyal Magma Cubes.
item.goety.flame_strike_focus.info: Summons Fire Pillars around the caster. Looking at a valid target and not crouching will surround them with Fire Pillars instead.
item.goety.soul_bolt_focus.info: Shoots a Soul Bolt that deals small magic damage and high knockback.
item.goety.magic_bolt_focus.info: Shoots a Magic Bolt that deals small magic damage and summons a small pool of damaging magic on a target that's hit by it.
item.goety.sword_focus.info: Shoots a magical duplicate of the caster's sword. Does nothing if caster is not wielding a sword off or main hand.
item.goety.frost_breath_focus.info: Shoots a torrent of frost in front of them, giving non-allied targets freezing damage.
item.goety.ice_spike_focus.info: Shoots an Ice Spike. Ice Spikes deals small freezing damage and gives target Freezing for a short time.
item.goety.ice_storm_focus.info: Shoots an Ice Storm that damages targets within its radius with freezing damage and gives Freezing for a short time. Can pass through blocks but moves slowly.
item.goety.hail_focus.info: Summons a cloud above a location or target that causes any non-allied targets beneath it to take freezing damage.
item.goety.updraft_focus.info: Summons a cloud of wind on a location or target that, after a time, shoots any target up in the air, damaging them.
item.goety.wind_blast_focus.info: Shoots a blast of wind that deals no damage to targets, but will knock them back.
item.goety.swarm_focus.info: Shoots a torrent of insects in front of the caster. Upon death, there's a chance an Insect Swarm will spawn on the target's position.
item.goety.grapple_focus.info: Shoots a vine hook that, when latched to a block, pulls the caster towards it.
item.goety.overgrowth_focus.info: Summons Quick Growing Vines at a location or surrounding a target. Cast crouching will summon a Poison-Quill Vine, that shoots poison quills at enemies.
item.goety.entangling_focus.info: Summons Entangle Vines on a target's feet or location. If the vines caught a target, they are immobilized in place.
item.goety.whispering_focus.info: Summons Whisperers. Cast crouching will summon the caster's servants towards them.
item.goety.shocking_focus.info: Shoots multiple electric currents at a non-allied target.
item.goety.charge_focus.info: Right-clicking on a mob or player will give them Charged and increase their Charged level. Charged I boosts Speed and Damage a bit, Charged II boosts Speed a lot but lowers Damage, giving another level will damage them.
item.goety.thunderbolt_focus.info: Shoots a large electric bolt at a non-allied target
item.goety.electrocute_focus.info: Shoots an electrical orb that, when looking at a target, follows them until it hits an object.
item.goety.monsoon_focus.info: Summons a cloud above a location or target that rains on targets beneath it and periodically shoots thunderbolts at them.
item.goety.discharge_focus.info: Summons a non-destructive electrical explosion on the caster, knocking back and damaging nearby non-allied targets.
item.goety.lightning_focus.info: Summons a Lightning Bolt at a location or target.
item.goety.shockwave_focus.info: Summons a non-destructive soul explosion on the caster, knocking back and damaging nearby non-allied targets.
item.goety.sonic_boom_focus.info: Shoots a Sonic Boom in front of them. Sonic Booms deals damage that goes through armor and enchantments.
item.goety.end_walk_focus.info: Renders caster completely invisible. Once effect ends or break, the caster teleports back to where the spell was cast.
item.goety.blink_focus.info: Teleports the caster to a location, or around a mob, they're looking at from a certain range. Crouch casting will cause the caster to teleport to a random location.
item.goety.banish_focus.info: Right-clicking on a mob or player will teleport them away from the caster.
item.goety.tunnel_focus.info: Summons an ethereal tunnel for a short while after right-clicking on a block, allowing entities to walk or fall through.
item.goety.soul_light_focus.info: Shoots a projectile that will create a dim ball of light when hit on a location.
item.goety.glow_light_focus.info: Shoots a projectile that will create a glowing ball of light when hit on a location.
item.goety.iron_hide_focus.info: Gives Iron Hide effect which increases caster's armor points.
item.goety.bulwark_focus.info: Gives magical shields that surrounds the caster. Taking damage from a mob or player will destroy a shield and knocks back the attacker.
item.goety.soul_heal_focus.info: Heals the caster from a range of an amount.
item.goety.telekinesis_focus.info: Targets an entity to float around the caster's crosshair.
item.goety.launch_focus.info: Launches the caster to the direction they're looking at.
item.goety.flying_focus.info: Fly at the direction the caster is looking at.
item.goety.cushion_focus.info: Summons a cloud on a location which will cause any entity that falls on it to not take fall damage.
item.goety.whirlwind_focus.info: Surrounds the caster in a whirlwind, which deflects nearby entities and slowly raise the caster up.
item.goety.cyclone_focus.info: Shoots a Cyclone that will cause any non-allied targets caught in it to be stuck and thrown.
item.goety.call_focus.info: Left-clicking on a servant will save it to the focus and make it active. Teleports the saved servant towards the caster.
item.goety.recall_focus.info: Right-clicking on certain blocks will save its position to the focus and make it active. Teleports the caster to the saved position.
item.goety.command_focus.info: Left-clicking on a servant will save it to the focus. Right-clicking on a block or entity will make the saved servant move to its position, right-clicking on a certain mob will cause the servant to attempt to ride on it.
item.goety.ender_chest_focus.info: Opens the caster's Ender Chest on their location.
item.goety.corruption_focus.info: Shoots out a beam of corruption that deals constant magic damage and ignores invulnerability frames.
effect.goety.summon_down.description: Spells cost more Soul Energy to cast, higher levels increases cost. Newly summoned Mobs will gain Sapped and Weakness.
effect.goety.sapped.description: Increases damage taken by 20% per level.
effect.goety.gold_touched.description: Mobs drop gold nuggets on death, with amount increasing on higher levels.
effect.goety.burn_hex.description: Removes Fire Resistance from living entities. On Hard, fire damage doubles.
effect.goety.soul_hunger.description: Weakens movement, mining and attack speed and melee damage.
effect.goety.buff.description: Increases melee attack damage by 0.5 hearts per level.
effect.goety.rampage.description: Increases melee attack damage by 0.5 heart per level, Increases mining and attack speed. Spawns an explosion after gaining 5 levels.
effect.goety.climbing.description: Grants ability to climb up horizontal walls and move through Cobwebs.
effect.goety.busted.description: Reduces armor points by 50% per level.
effect.goety.soul_armor.description: Increases armor points by 2. Triples armor points if affected entities does not wear any armor.
effect.goety.iron_hide.description: Increases armor points by 4 per level.
effect.goety.pressure.description: Creepers will explode nigh-instantly towards targets with this effect.
effect.goety.charged.description: Level I gives 10% boost to speed and melee damage, Level II gives 25% boost to speed and reduction in melee damage. Gaining another Level will give damage.
effect.goety.ender_ground.description: Prevents teleportation unless it's by chat command.
effect.goety.freezing.description: Simulate being in powdered snow. Does nothing if immune to freezing.
effect.goety.nyctophobia.description: Periodically deals damage when in dark areas.
effect.goety.sun_allergy.description: Sets the affected entities on fire and damages helmet when in daylight.
effect.goety.snow_skin.description: Gives characteristics of Snow Golems to affected entities.
effect.goety.tripping.description: Causes the affected entities to be pushed in random direction periodically, higher levels makes it more frequent.
effect.goety.arrowmantic.description: Attract arrows towards the affected entities. Higher levels increases the radius.
effect.goety.sense_loss.description: Gives players blindness and causes mobs to have lower visibility range, with higher levels lowering it further.
effect.goety.flame_hands.description: Physical attacks sets entities aflame for 4 seconds with each level increasing the duration.
effect.goety.venomous_hands.description: Physical attacks gives Poison for 10 seconds with each level increasing the level.
effect.goety.repulsive.description: Knocks back attacking entity away; higher levels increases knockback distance.
effect.goety.explosive.description: Have a chance of unleashing an explosion when hurt; higher levels increases chance and explosion strength.
effect.goety.insight.description: Doubles the amount of experience points dropped; higher levels increases yield.
effect.goety.fire_trail.description: Walking sets the ground beneath on fire.
effect.goety.fiery_aura.description: Sets nearby entities on fire; higher levels increases range and burn duration.
effect.goety.frosty_aura.description: Gives nearby entities Freezing; higher levels increases range and Freezing level.
effect.goety.plunge.description: Causes flying or swimming affected entities to drop towards the ground.
effect.goety.photosynthesis.description: Regenerates health when in sunlight; higher levels make health regenerate quicker.
effect.goety.flammable.description: Affected entities take more damage from fire; does not effect fire resistant entities.
effect.goety.save_effects.description: Effects persists after affected player's death. Does nothing if player is in hardcore.
effect.goety.wild_rage.description: Affected entities will target and attack any nearby attackable entities.
effect.goety.stunned.description: Stops affected from doing anything like moving, attacking or using blocks or items.
effect.goety.shadow_walk.description: Grants true invisibility. Removed when interacting with blocks, entities or items. Multiplies attack damage while under the effect.
effect.goety.doom.description: Once effect expires, deals instant death if affected is on low health. Bosses cannot be effected.
effect.goety.fortunate.description: Increases Fortune level for affected. Increases by effect level.
effect.goety.corpse_eater.description: Restores hunger and saturation with each kill.
effect.goety.acid_venom.description: Inflicts non lethal damage over time; higher levels do more damage per second. Does affect Undead
effect.goety.spasms.description: Inflicts non lethal damage over time, pushing affected in random direction when inflicted; higher levels do more damage per second.
enchantment.goety.soul_eater.desc: Increases the amount of Soul Energy gained after killing a mob.
enchantment.goety.wanting.desc: Mobs will drop more loot when killed via Summoned Creatures/Spells.
enchantment.goety.burning.desc: Makes Spells burn mobs or increase duration of fire.
enchantment.goety.absorb.desc: Causes the player to heal when Spells damages mob.
enchantment.goety.velocity.desc: Increases the speed and velocity of magic projectiles.
info.goety.items.dark_scroll.desc: Must be used within a Woodland Mansion.

info.goety.items.blaze_horn.desc: Must be used within a Nether Fortress.
info.goety.items.blaze_horn.failure: You are not within a Nether Fortress!

info.goety.items.buried: Some sort of ancient manuscript of a nameless kingdom...
info.goety.items.front: A repurposed spell of a nameless king...
info.goety.items.floral: Old rites for whispering to the flora.
info.goety.items.terminus: The schematics of a terrifying monstrosity...

info.goety.research.warred: You have learned the method of making Redstone Golems!
info.goety.research.buried: You have learned the nameless paths of Necromancy!
info.goety.research.haunting: You have learned the method of possessing Armors!
info.goety.research.front: You have learned the method of summoning Vanguards!
info.goety.research.mistral: You have learned the method of constructing Squall Golems!
info.goety.research.floral: You have learned the method of creating Whisperers and Leapleaves!

info.goety.research.lich: You have learned the secret to Immortality!
info.goety.dark_hat: Halves casting time for all spells.
info.goety.grand_turban: Have a chance of spawning an allied Irk when taking damage.
info.goety.witch_hat: Speeds up witches robes inner brewing stand. Slowly grants fuel in moonlight
info.goety.necro_crown_cast: Halves casting time for necromancy spells.
info.goety.amethyst_necklace: +20% chance summoning four Totemic Bombs casting Barricade spell.
info.goety.amethyst_necklace_discount: Halves soul cost of geomancy spells.
info.goety.dark_robe: Reduces soul cost of all spells by 15%.
info.goety.grand_robe: Halves incoming attacks when casting with wand or staff.
info.goety.necro_cape: Allows undead servants heal using soul energy.
info.goety.necro_cape_power: Certain newly summoned undead servants gain extra abilities.
info.goety.frost_robe: +%s%% resistance to freezing damage, immunity to powder snow.
info.goety.frost_robe_discount: Halves soul cost of frost spells.
info.goety.wild_robe: Immunity to poison and acid venom. Allows natural servants heal using soul energy.
info.goety.wild_robe_discount: Halves soul cost of wild spells.
info.goety.wind_robe: Provides slow fall at a cost of soul energy, immunity to fall damage.
info.goety.wind_robe_discount: Halves soul cost of wind spells.
info.goety.storm_robe_discount: Halves soul cost of storm spells.
info.goety.witch_robe_brew: Press %s to open robe brewing stand.
info.goety.warlock_garment: Automatically uses Wartful Eggs when afflicted with negative effect.
info.goety.warlock_robe: +%s%% resistance to magical damage. Arthopods are neutral to wearer.
info.goety.ring_of_want: When enchanted with Wanting, increases looting level when killing with servants or spells.
info.goety.wayfarers_belt: Increases movement and swimming speed, step and jump height.
info.goety.spiteful_belt: Hurt attackers with thorn damage when taking damage.
info.goety.star_amulet: Protects against arrows when below half the max health.
info.goety.alarming_charm: Warns when an Illager assault has appeared.
info.goety.ominous_saddle: Saddles tamed Ravagers and increases their max health.
info.goety.ice_bouquet_trap: Summons an Ice Bouquet on top of it, which damages entities with frost damage.
info.goety.ice_bouquet_trap_extra: Requires a redstone pulse to activate.
info.goety.wind_blower: Pushes entities away from it depending on its orientation. The distance equals the redstone power it receives.
info.goety.sculk_devourer: Transforms experience dropped by recently killed mobs into soul energy and gives it to the placer.
info.goety.sculk_devourer_extra: Can be enchanted with Soul Eater and Radius.
info.goety.sculk_converter: Absorbs soul energy, from a filled Cursed Cage above it, to spread sculk.
info.goety.sculk_converter_extra: Requires a redstone pulse to activate. Can be enchanted with Potency.
info.goety.sculk_relay: Sculk Converters will spread sculk on a nearby relay's location.
info.goety.sculk_grower: Absorbs soul energy, from a filled Cursed Cage above it, to increase growth speed of surrounding crops.
info.goety.sculk_grower_extra: Activates with redstone. Can be enchanted with Potency and Radius.
info.goety.forbidden_grass: Quickly spawns monsters on it. Will be set aflame in sunlight or near fire.
info.goety.hook_bell: When rung, teleports raiders near the bell. Can only be rung manually.
info.goety.haunted_glass: Players can pass through but not mobs.
info.goety.haunted_glass_tinted: Players can pass through but not mobs. Blocks light.
info.goety.haunted_glass_mob: Mobs can pass through but not players.
info.goety.haunted_glass_mob_tinted: Mobs can pass through but not players. Blocks light.
info.goety.freezing_lamp: Slowly freezes nearby water to ice and puts snow on the surrounding area.
info.goety.apparition_door: Vanishes when right-clicked or powered. Will reappear after a short while.
info.goety.ritual.fail: You do not know how to properly start this ritual!
info.goety.ritual.tooManyItems.fail: Too many Items on Pedestals within Vicinity!

advancements.goety.root.title: The Dark Arts
advancements.goety.craft_totem_roots.des: Craft a Totem of Roots, which can be used to craft basic components.
advancements.goety.craft_infuser.title: Cursed Elements
advancements.goety.craft_infuser.descrip: Put it on a Spawner to make it work.
advancements.goety.craft_magic_emerald.d: Looks like there's something more to Emeralds than previously thought...
advancements.goety.craft_totem.title: Make Your Own
advancements.goety.craft_cursed_ingot.de: Seems to be what Spawners are made of.
advancements.goety.craft_empty_focus.des: Maybe make a Wand first before anything else.
advancements.goety.craft_dark_wand.title: Oh, the Pointing Again.
advancements.goety.craft_dark_robe.title: Look at Me, I'm the Evoker Now
advancements.goety.craft_dark_robe.descr: Dark Hats reduces Casting Time, Dark Robes reduces Soul Costs.
Craft an Animation Core through a Ritual.
advancements.goety.craft_vexing_focus.de: Look out for any Hermits outside of your windows.
advancements.goety.craft_biting_focus.de: Perhaps it can be improved later on...
advancements.goety.craft_all_focus.title: Hyperfocus
advancements.goety.craft_dark_altar.desc: Place the Dark Altar onto a Cursed Cage with a Totem of Souls in it.
advancements.goety.craft_necro_brazier.d: Needs to be placed within the Deep Dark, on top of a Cursed Cage with Totem or Transfer Gem.
advancements.goety.craft_dark_scythe.des: Grants Soul Energy with each hit. Attack Speed increases if not holding anything offhand.
advancements.goety.craft_star_amulet.des: Protects wearer from arrows when under half the max health.
advancements.goety.craft_ring_of_want.de: Increases Loot Drop from Mobs when killed using Spells or Summons. Must be enchanted first.
advancements.goety.craft_ring_of_force.d: Using Telekinesis spell on a mob or player will cause them to slowly lose breath and chock.
advancements.goety.craft_ring_of_the_dra: Powers up Fire and Frost Breath Spells.
advancements.goety.craft_sculk_converter: Absorbs Soul Energy, from the Cursed Cage above it, to grow Sculk around itself.
advancements.goety.craft_sculk_grower.de: Absorbs a certain amount of Soul Energy to grow surrounding crops.
advancements.goety.craft_resonance_cryst: Left-click on Squall Golem to bind it to it. Activated by Wind Blowers.
advancements.goety.craft_arca.title: Remote Connection
advancements.goety.craft_arca.descriptio: The Arca stores and distributes your Soul Energy without a need of a Totem of Souls.
advancements.goety.craft_witch_hat.title: We've Found a Witch!
advancements.goety.craft_witch_hat.descr: Craft or find a Witches Hat, which gives a chance of not consuming a Potion.
advancements.goety.craft_witch_robe.desc: Witches Robes gives 85% magic protection and portable brewing. Wearing both Robe and Hat makes Witches neutral.
advancements.goety.craft_necro_set.title: Really Late Healer
advancements.goety.craft_necro_set.descr: Wearing Necro Crown and Cape causes none boss Undead to be Neutral. Necro Staff powers Necromantic Spells.
advancements.goety.craft_nameless_set.de: Nameless Crown and Cape have same benefits as the Necro set. Nameless Staff powers Necromantic and certain Spells.
advancements.goety.craft_illusion_robe.d: Improves Invisibility effect and Mirror Spells.
advancements.goety.craft_frost_robe.desc: Frost Robes grants resistance to freeze damage and gives discount to Frost Spells.
advancements.goety.craft_wild_robe.title: Where The Wild Things At?
advancements.goety.craft_wild_robe.descr: Wild Robes grants immunity to Poison and Acid Venom and gives discount to Wild Spells.
advancements.goety.craft_wind_robe.title: It Wimdy
advancements.goety.craft_wind_robe.descr: Wind Robes slows down descent and gives discount to Wind Spells.
advancements.goety.craft_storm_robe.desc: Storm Robes slows down descent and gives discount to Storm Spells.
advancements.goety.craft_all_robes.title: Fancy Wardrobe
advancements.goety.kill_envioker.title: Angry Video Game Illager
